description: Navigate to Buckeye Rd & 4th Av. The route begins at the intersection of S Montezuma Ave and Buckeye Rd, marked by a modern white building on the corner. Proceed east along Buckeye Rd, keeping the white building and a large wooden construction site on the right. The path continues straight along the sidewalk for a short distance.
